message.entry: Arguments must be a scalar or have the same length.
Multiple shapes must be specified as a cell array.
Too many obstacles for the provided map size, either reduce number of obstacles, increase map size, or increase map resolution.
Shapes argument must be a nonempty string scalar, string array, or cell array of character vectors.
Each shape type must be specified only once.
Number of elements in shapes must be less than or equal to 3.
The shapes {0} are ignored because the number of obstacles is less than the number of shapes.
